    "body" : "<p>Guava: <a href=\"https://google.github.io/guava/releases/19.0/api/docs/com/google/common/math/DoubleMath.html#isMathematicalInteger(double)\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>DoubleMath.isMathematicalInteger</code></a>.  (Disclosure: I wrote it.)  Or, if you aren't already importing Guava, <code>x == Math.rint(x)</code> is the fastest way to do it; <code>rint</code> is measurably faster than <code>floor</code> or <code>ceil</code>.</p>\n"
