    "body" : "<p>Because of <code>%</code> operator cannot apply to BigDecimal and int (i.e. 1) directly, so I am using the following snippet to check if the BigDecimal is an integer:</p>\n<pre><code>value.stripTrailingZeros().scale() &lt;= 0\n</code></pre>\n"
